5. Shortcut keys and so on

ESC+F10 = exit
CTRL-ESC = iconify

- - - - -

6. What can I run it with?

You should be able to run the game on all the most common operating 
systems you can get all the needed SDL packages for. Our beta testers have 
reported it to work at least on Win32, Linux, PPC970 (G5), UltraSparcII.
It should be very portable. :)

- - - - -

7. License / Copying

In case you happen to sell the game, you must sell it without the wav-files in data/-directory. ^^
Some stuff there aren't under GPL but under some "free, but only for personal use" license.

For everything but not those wav-files, see the file "COPYING"

