9. Changes

1.3.1
- Changed message sending to enter instead of chatkey
- Fixed the space bug in the nickname bar in the menu
- Added a cool (eh..) sound to tell when another player joins
- Made cpu usage lower in the "waiting for another player" screen

1.3.0u2
- Added possibility to compile without sounds

1.3.0u
- Added support for big endian

1.3.0
- Lots of stuff



